item.description:
Welcome to the only indoor doubles opportunity in Massachusetts.

Time: 2PM - 4PM.
Cap: 6 A/AA players.

Court: Standard 9m x 9m court. Floor material is MaxxPlay, a seamless polyurethane surface which exhibits excellent shock absorbent and slide characteristics. If we get 3 women, we can lower net to women's height and play CR.

Ruleset: http://www.meetup.com...
Format: Scrimmage/practice. 21-point sets. Different partner each set.
Ball: Wilson AVP

Optionally, you can also play pickup sixes noon-2PM for an additional $5 paid at the entry window.

Sign up as an individual. To apply, please email your doubles experience (including level BB/A/AA/O) and your email address.
Email Matt at: http://volleyball.mee...
item.name: Advanced Indoor Doubles
